-- Shell climate change litigation story withdrawn
-- 
-- Thu Mar 15, 2012 6:47am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/15/us-shell-climate-idUSBRE82E0CM20120315

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - The story headlined "Shell says being sued for causing climate change" is wrong. The reference made by the company in its annual report referred to lawsuits that are already in the public domain. The story has been withdrawn. 
